 Police operatives in Lagos State have once again arrested Nollywood actress, Yetunde Akilapa, for theft. It was gathered that the actress, who is notorious for breaking into houses and stores to steal, was arrested on Thursday, February 16, 2023. According to Twitter personality Noor, she entered her apartment and found Akilapa inside, she was going through her things looking for what to steal. ALSO READ:  Man caught despite disguising self as a sheep to escape prison Recall that in 2015, she was arrested while br£aking into a beauty lounge with a master key, after closing hours in Yaba, where she worked. Fast forward to 2018, the actress was once again arrested for trying to gain unlawful access into a house in Magodo area of Lagos. 